snippet.title: GRID | Race For Glory Trailer [UK] | #LikeNoOther
snippet.description:
Race. Compete. Enjoy. Do it all #LikeNoOther. 

Watch the first gameplay trailer for GRID, launching this October for Xbox One, PS4 and PC. Also coming to Google Stadia. 🏁 

Pre-order ⬇️ 

Steam: http://bit.ly/GRIDSteam
PS4: http://bit.ly/GRIDPS4
Xbox: http://bit.ly/GRIDXbox

Read more ➡️ http://blog.codemasters.com/grid/07/grid-first-gameplay-trailer-and-likenoother
